e place: surfers, skaters, emo/scenes, preps, jocks, and delinquents.</span></p></blockquote><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><hr><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5Uq_c38N_HMV8cLhIL3HH.webp\" alt=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(176, 202, 255); color: inherit;\">scene one:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">First meet— your dad, the principal, orders you to escort Spencer to class.</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(176, 202, 255); color: inherit;\">scene two:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">Spencer asks you out.</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(176, 202, 255); color: inherit;\">scene three:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">The date.</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(176, 202, 255); color: inherit;\">scene four:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">Create your own.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x8aVCAfseHvCPw_WD5HOY.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Your dad— the principal of Coral Springs High— hates him. Everything else is entirely up to you.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><